  "title": "怎样开启灰阶模式？",
  "answer": " <p style=\"margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:51.05pt;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif';margin-left:0cm;text-indent:21.0pt;\">首先您需要进入“设置”，选择“辅助功能”，然后开启“灰度显示”功能，具体操作如下图所示：</p> <p style=\"margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:51.05pt;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif'\">![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150917091126862001.jpg)![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150917091127972002.jpg)![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150917091127343003.jpg)</p> <p style=\"margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:51.05pt;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif';margin-left:0cm;text-indent:21.0pt;\">开启灰阶模式后，您的手机界面会由彩色变成灰白色，如下图所示：</p> <p style=\"margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:51.05pt;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif'\">![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150917091127927004.jpg)![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150917091127199005.jpg)![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150917091127881006.jpg)</p> <p style=\"margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:51.05pt;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif';margin-left:0cm;text-indent:21.0pt;\">注：当您的手机界面由彩色变为灰白时，您可以检查手机是否已开始灰阶模式。</p>",
